Class PISAXHandler

java.lang.Object
  org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      evs.data.fileio.PISAXHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler
public class PISAXHandler
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler

Handler for time-series files in the Published Interface (PI) XML format, for which a schema is available from: http://fews.wldelft.nl/schemas/version1.0/pi-schemas/pi_timeseries.xsd Reads files containing ensemble forecasts and files containing observations.

Author:
evs@hydrosolved.com
